This paper involves computer vision (CV) techniques such as Part Affinity Field and deep learning models like Residual Convolutional Neural Network, Region Proposal Network, and Recurrent Neural Network. Therefore, it is highly likely to belong to the cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) sub-category. Additionally, the paper involves artificial intelligence (AI) methodologies, which makes it likely to belong to the cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) sub-category. The paper also has applications in robotics (cs.RO), and the use of RF signals involves signal processing and machine learning techniques (cs.NE). Finally, the paper involves the creation of a simulator, which falls under the cs.MM (Multimedia) sub-category.
